column1: For people who are wondering why the mail ballot count is mostly favoring Democrats — it’s because Donald Trump demonized mail voting and told his supporters to vote in person.   Plus more Democrats have been concerned about catching COVID-19 by voting in person. #Biden2020

I believe Democrats have a good chance of picking up 4-6 Congressional seats in Texas this year. Delegation could be 18-18.  We have excellent candidates Republican incumbents dragged down by President Trump and Texans fed up of the botched Coronavirus response by Trump/Abbott. https://t.co/20hACbS4vl
